<SceneText>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>クレス</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Cless</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>チェスター</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Chester</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>これでよかったんだよね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm glad we managed.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ったくよ。　お前は気を遣いすぎなんだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Geez. You're too considerate.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>過去を変えたいと思う気持ち……。
それは僕達も彼らも
きっと同じなのに……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The feeling of wanting to change the past...
I'm sure it's the same for them as it is for us...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>同じモン欲しがりゃ
どっちかが泣く事になんのは
しかたねぇだろ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If people want the same thing, it's a given that
someone's gonna end up upset about it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いちいち気にしてたらきりがねぇよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If you're concerned about every one of them,
you'll never see the end of it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そうだね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're right...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いこう、チェスター。
僕達には、他人を押しやってでも
叶えたい願いがあるんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's go, Chester. Even if we have to
push others aside for it, we have a
wish we want granted.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そういうことだ。
立ち止まってる暇なんかないぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Exactly. We don't have the time to be stopping.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Unreferenced</Section>
